## Part 1

```elixir
batteries
|> Enum.map(fn battery ->
  max_first = battery |> Enum.take(Enum.count(battery) - 1) |> Enum.max()
  max_second = battery |> Enum.drop_while(&(&1 != max_first)) |> Enum.drop(1) |> Enum.max()
  Integer.undigits([max_first, max_second])
end)
